WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.830
Marketing tadqiqot uchun mijoz yaratishda,

00:00:01.830 --> 00:00:06.180
Siz shunchaki faraziy Becky nimani 
xohlashini va kiyinishini tasavvur qilasiz

00:00:06.180 --> 00:00:09.375
u qaerda xarid qiladi va nega u sizning 
kompaniyangiz mijozi bo‘lishni xohlashi mumkin.

00:00:09.375 --> 00:00:13.480
Biz buni mijozimizdan olingan haqiqiy 
ma’lumotlar asosida bajaramiz.

00:00:13.480 --> 00:00:15.565
LinkedIn ma’lumotlaridan 
foydalanib tahlil qilamiz.

00:00:15.565 --> 00:00:17.540
Bu ularning yoshi, bu 
ularning lavozimi.

00:00:17.540 --> 00:00:20.640
Biz haqiqiy ma’lumotlarga asoslanib 
mijoz uchun personajlar yaratamiz.

00:00:20.640 --> 00:00:22.060
Mening ismim Emili Peters.

00:00:22.060 --> 00:00:25.695
Men Uncommon Bold brendi strategiyachisi 
va asoschisiman.

00:00:25.695 --> 00:00:28.230
Uncommon Bold - bu brend 
strategiyasi studiyasi.

00:00:28.230 --> 00:00:31.170
Biz kompaniyalarga tushunmovchilik 
vaziyatida yordam beramiz.

00:00:31.170 --> 00:00:35.085
Bir necha xil tahlillarni qilamiz va 
keyin ularga yo‘l tanlashda yordam beramiz

00:00:35.085 --> 00:00:37.020
bu yo‘l ularga

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:39.344
haqiqatan ham mijozlar oson 
tushunadigan va yoqtiradigan, 

00:00:39.344 --> 00:00:43.125
raqobatbardosh mahsulot yaratish, 
tonnalab daromad keltirsh, 

00:00:43.125 --> 00:00:45.895
kompaniyalariga minglab odam jalb qilishga 
imkon beradigan yo‘l bo‘ladi deb umid qilamiz.

00:00:45.895 --> 00:00:50.400
Mening mijozlarim barcha shifokorlar, olimlar va muhandislar,

00:00:50.400 --> 00:00:52.425
ularning barchasi ma’lumotlar bilan ishlaydi.

00:00:52.425 --> 00:00:55.800
Mening usulim - media bilan taqdim etilgan 

00:00:55.800 --> 00:01:00.390
juda batafsil ma’lumotlar tahlil 

00:01:00.390 --> 00:01:02.430
shunchaki raqamlar emas.

00:01:02.430 --> 00:01:04.980
Biz juda sodda algoritm yaratdik, 

00:01:04.980 --> 00:01:06.420
u mijozlar uchun juda qulay va ko‘rgazmali

00:01:06.420 --> 00:01:10.170
faoliyatining sonli ko‘rsatkichlarini oyma-oy 
ko‘rishga va tahlil qilishga imkon beradi.

00:01:10.170 --> 00:01:11.760
Men buni birinchi marta ishlab chiqqanimda

00:01:11.760 --> 00:01:15.870
uning ta’siri juda katta bo‘lgan. 
Juda sodda, oson tushunarli formula, 

00:01:15.870 --> 00:01:20.185
lekin ilgari hech kim foydalanmagan.

00:01:20.185 --> 00:01:23.920
Men buni o‘z veb-saytimga joylashtirganman 
va hozir ko‘p odamlar undan foydalanishmoqda.

00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:25.740
Men uchun odamlar ishini namoyish 
qilishini yengillashtirib, 

00:01:25.740 --> 00:01:28.590
ularga yordam berayotganimni 
his qilish juda yoqimli.

00:01:28.590 --> 00:01:31.485
Hamma narsani boshqarish va o‘lchash kerak.

00:01:31.485 --> 00:01:34.260
Ma’lumotlar yordamida siz 
aslida orqaga qaytib, 

00:01:34.260 --> 00:01:35.655
raqamlarga chuqurroq qarashingiz mumkin,

00:01:35.655 --> 00:01:39.510
shunchaki fikrlarga emas, 
haqiqiy ma’lumotlarga asoslanib 

00:01:39.510 --> 00:01:43.590
mijoz bilan unumli 
suhbatlashishingiz mumkin.

00:01:43.590 --> 00:01:46.320
Siz kasbiy yo‘lingizda ma’lumotlarga 
tayanmasligingiz ham mumkin.

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:48.720
Ammo, agar siz raqamlarni birlashtirib

00:01:48.720 --> 00:01:51.660
slayd yoki grafik ko‘rinishida 
taqdim eta olsangiz,

00:01:51.660 --> 00:01:53.820
bu chindan ham sizga odamlarni 
siz xohlagan yo‘nalishdan yurishiga 

00:01:53.820 --> 00:01:57.680
ishontirish qobiliyatingizni oshiradi.

